This is a (almost) straight port to GWT of PrettyTime - http://ocpsoft.com/prettytime/

It's an Eclipse project, but I don't see why the source as such shouldn't be usable outside Eclipse. If you create 


Still lacking translations to any languages outside English. Will add the translations provided by PrettyTime once I've ironed out some of the bugs.

Anyone knows how to compile jar-files for the modules? I'd like to provide those for people who're not interested in developing this GWT module, just use it.